align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Instagram and Linkedin as a social media manager. You can make other</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">additions if you’re able to take them up.:</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 0.8759994506835938pt;margin-top:20.438552856445312pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Step 3: </span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Customize Your Profile</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019388198852538;margin-left: 0.8639984130859375pt;margin-right: 19.9094