(19, 22, 'Target audience', 'video', '6081728901889.mp4', NULL, NULL, '5:35', '7365535', '2024-10-14 02:16:14', '2024-10-14 17:31:29', NULL),
(20, 23, 'How to find a target audience', 'video', '5621728901928.mp4', NULL, NULL, '8:57', '12370211', '2024-10-14 02:16:54', '2024-10-14 17:32:08', NULL),
(21, 24, 'Tools for social media management', 'text', NULL, NULL, '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019466876983641;margin-left: 72.2750015258789pt;margin-right: 1.9232177734375pt;text-indent: 0.43999481201171875pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Social media management plays a crucial role in effectively managing and growing a brand\'s presence on various social media platforms and it can sometimes be overwhelming. To achieve this, social media managers rely on a variety of tools that help streamline their workflow, enhance content creation and scheduling, analyze performance, engage with the community, and more.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019479751586914;margin-left: 72.22000122070312pt;margin-right: 4.2681884765625pt;text-indent: 0.4069976806640625pt;margin-top:18.7354736328125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">These tools are like helpful assistants that make it easier to organize, schedule, and analyze your social media activities. In this lesson, we will explore different tools that can simplify your social media management tasks.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 91.26499938964844pt;margin-top:36.36383056640625pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">1. Content Creation Tools:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019452571868895;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 2.67852783203125pt;margin-top:4.791534423828125pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Canva: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.canva.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> This tool allows you to create eye-catching graphics and designs for your social media posts, even if you have no design experience. </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Adobe Spark: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.adobe.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Similar to Canva, Adobe Spark offers easy-to-use design features to create visually appealing images, videos, and web pages for social media.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 90.6709976196289pt;margin-top:36.363922119140625pt;margin-b