pan><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Mention allows you to monitor social media mentions and conversations about your brand, industry, or relevant keywords. It helps you stay informed about what people are saying and engage in conversations.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.601946973800659;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 3.63848876953125pt;text-indent: -17.394996643066406pt;margin-top:1.107025146484375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.394996643066406pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Sprout Social: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.sproutsocial.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> Besides analytics, Sprout Social also offers tools for managing your social media community. It allows you to schedule and publish posts, monitor messages and comments, and engage with your audience all in one place.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019466876983641;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 34.19500732421875pt;text-indent: -17.449996948242188pt;margin-top:1.106903076171875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.449996948242188pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Hootsuite: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.hootsuite.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> In addition to scheduling, Hootsuite provides features for social media monitoring, allowing you to listen to conversations, respond to comments, and engage with your audience effectively.&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-left: 90.68199920654297pt;margin-top:36.36395263671875pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">5. Social Media Advertising Tools:&nbsp;</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019498348236083;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;margin-right: 18.533203125pt;text-indent: -17.031997680664062pt;margin-top:4.791351318359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.031997680664062pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Facebook Ads Manager: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.facebook.com/business/tools/ads-manager</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">)</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> If you\'re running Facebook or Instagram ads, Facebook Ads Manager provides a platform to create, manage, and track your ad campaigns. It allows you to target specific audiences, set budgets, and monitor ad performance.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-3ccabe2d-7fff-ae76-09ea-73419303318b\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.6019442558288575;margin-left: 90.95700073242188pt;text-indent: -17.692001342773438pt;margin-top:1.10693359375pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.692001342773438pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">● </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:700;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Upfluence: </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#1155cc;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:underline;-webkit-text-decoration-skip:none;text-decoration-skip-ink:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">www.upfluence.com</span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:\'Comic Sans MS\',sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">) Upfluence helps you discover and connect with relevant social media influencers for potential collaborations and influencer marketing campaigns. It provides influencer data, performance metrics, and contact information.</span></p>', '', '', '2024-10-14 02:18:03', '2024-10-14 02:18:03', NULL),
